    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Too often when people provide a service (be it making an ad, writing an email, or creating a product) they do a sloppy job.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That’s because they compromise on quality, (often) hoping their customers or viewers won’t notice.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Of course, if you wouldn’t eagerly want to read your content, listen to yourself speak, or buy your products, how can you possibly expect other people will either?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The golden rule isn’t just a nice thing to do, it’s the most important metric for any service or business seeking to sustain itself.",
